response.original_title: 理芽 3rd ONE-MAN LIVE 「ニューロマンスIII」
response.overview: Virtual singer RIM has previously held two solo online concerts, and now she will host her first live audience event, 'RIM 3rd ONE-MAN LIVE "NEUROMANCE III"!'  This concert marks the third installment of KAMITSUBAKI STUDIO's "KAMITSUBAKI WARS 2024" series, titled "KAMITSUBAKI KORAKUEN BATTLEFRONT." It will take place at TOKYO DOME CITY HALL, along with the previous day's KAF & RIM TWO-MAN LIVE "Singularity Live Vol.3."  This first live audience solo concert is going to surpass her previous online performances.
response.title: RIM 3rd ONE-MAN LIVE「NEUROMANCE III」
